data.description: This adorable home is waiting for you!  Fantastic home next to Liberty Park and steps to one of the many catch and release ponds in the neighborhood.  Kitchen has white cabinets and granite.  Backyard has a covered patio and full sprinkler.  This master planned community has pool, waterslide, tennis, basketball court, and gym.  On the power grid with power plant so does not loose power during blackouts!
